{"tid":1019631,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【斷老公財路後】稱婚姻忍讓不是必然 吳若希：別為不愛的男人卑躬屈膝","createTime":"2019-02-13T05:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T09:30:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fbdafc9fe5cb65f29f227537d44dcb829497827b","tid":1019631,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:27:14.000Z","msg":"自稱「釣蝦女皇Queen of釣蝦」的吳若希，經常在社交網分享與老公何兆鴻（Alex）的生活點滴（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Bx9NHy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Bx9NHy&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwieIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=b2206d73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Bx9NHy</a> ），她昨晚在facebook貼出《如懿傳》主題曲《日月存亡》MV，留言：「一根刺，種下後會慢慢發芽，到它長大後，會變成刀，婚姻中的忍讓不是必然，現實不是宮廷劇，夫妻關係也不再是日月存亡。對不起，我不認同妻子要為不愛（不懂愛）她的男人卑躬屈膝。」究竟她是暗示與何兆鴻（Alex）婚變，還是借老公博宣傳！？<br />\n吳若希一向有老公萬事足，常把Alex掛在嘴邊，她一時說老公對她千依百順，甚至自認被寵愛到有公主癌，一時又爆曾被老公背叛，到BB出世時才原諒對方，一時又化身「豬隊友」斷老公財路，試過霸氣警告老公客戶「齋吹水、冇行動的客人、不要再打給我老公」，以免影響她的度假心情，而Alex家境不俗，在澳門從事洋酒代理、搞團購網，還有入股某品牌眼鏡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190213/large/1550027941_907a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190213%2Flarge%2F1550027941_907a.jpg&h=04940d07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68f38a8b2dceb5b9557328c7484d80c9429958bd","tid":1019631,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:44:53.000Z","msg":"佢老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好明顯女強男弱<br />\n個男成日頭茸茸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e244cba2d37bf2b88196ee5d67f6dca732ee8cc6","tid":1019631,"uid":128111,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"講乜撚原唔原諒，其實嫁佢都係為錢啫，人點對人，人咪點對你囉，臭雞"},{"pid":"940488e8d2fd854ff329cd9ace7f7dc83a4e2d1e","tid":1019631,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68f38a8b2dceb5b9557328c7484d80c9429958bd","tid":1019631,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:44:53.000Z","msg":"佢老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好明顯女強男弱<br />\n個男成日頭茸茸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:29:51.000Z","msg":"個男既連吳若希都娶得落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc95d75ddd52b1caeb57d048c5d106e5c92e8dfc","tid":1019631,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"378647517870f3d56161fcdcc44fe0268e8bc200","tid":1019631,"uid":124372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T09:30:03.000Z","msg":"下一個目標係咩呀？<br />\nmk妹：梗係離婚分身家做女強人啦，I am queen of港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}